</p>

<p> At Lytx, I had the wonderful opportunity to work on various projects with a very talented and diverse team. Working together with my Scrum team, which included UX, QA, developers, and our project manager, I was able to learn a lot about using the Scaled Agile Framework to develop a SAAS product. 
</p>
<p>
