notes. And after the trip, it was my job to consolidate my notes, and summarize the most relevant findings. 
</p>

<h2 class="chance">Transitioning: Phase III</h2>

<p>After usability testing, the first thing we do is make any necessary revisions. These can range from small changes, like increasing the font type to bigger changes like re-ordering the navigation. Then we work on finalizng
